title: The Nebula’s Civilization
description: The Nebula’s Civilization Manhwa 슬기로운 문명생활, Nebula’s Civilization Choi Seong-woon, achieves the top rank in the game “Lost World,” successfully completing all the game’s achievements. However, his joy doesn’t last long when he receives a suspicious email and is summoned to the real “Lost World,” where he embarks on a competition to become a “god.”
